{
  "_note": "Synthetic vectors. Inputs derived from the upstream TTN examples (Apache-2.0); expected.data authored to the normalized vocabulary and cross-checked against reference/upstream-codec.js field extraction. Battery = bytes[0] * 10 mV / 1000 -> V. The Device_State frame supplies action.motion.detected + action.motion.count; the Acceleration_Data frame supplies action.motion.detected; together they cover the `motion` category requires path (action.motion).",
